{"tid":1191004,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"2014年無限之戰輸咗，2019年終局之戰要贏返","createTime":"2019-06-07T16:25:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-08T05:59:09.000Z","uid":222524,"like":72,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"7820b68829ff3cb26f1395d70f18c03168d3064e","tid":1191004,"uid":222524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T16:25:52.000Z","msg":"2014年既傘運，我地好似avenger咁，俾Thanos逐個據點擊破<br />\n係呢幾年，唔同人都有唔同反應<br />\n有人好似Hawkeye咁，做咗勇武激進派<br />\n都有人好似Iron Man咁，灰晒心，俾當年既失敗同無力感導致縮咗幾年<br />\n但唔緊要！<br />\n無論你係Hawkeye定Iron Man，6月9日至少會有成班Avengers會出黎<br />\n我地今次仲集齊到美國，德國，歐盟呢d無限寶石<br />\n你唔洗再驚！<br />\n就算你係Hawkeye咁既普通人，係endgame大戰入面攬住手套跑全場，都希望你出黎<br />\n唔好令一班獄中義士白白犧牲<br />\n同時都要阻止再有一班義士，係未來被人送去獄中，不論係送去香港定中國<br />\n<br />\n失去既，我地要攞返；現有既，我地要盡力保存，at all cost<br />\nAnd maybe not die trying would be nice.<br />\n6月9號，Whatever it takes"},{"pid":"4231c41ebdaa57c5a3b260254ebcd7f70de477f5","tid":1191004,"uid":19278,"like":21,"dislike":3,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T16:29:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KoSBzST.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKoSBzST.gif&h=a5774beb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"944603143818a5644b51501cbcb91268967b2cbe","tid":1191004,"uid":4739,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T16:32:15.000Z","msg":"屌你劇透"},{"pid":"e2789ea9043f91a6e48517f168ea208b4945be04","tid":1191004,"uid":10670,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T16:35:22.000Z","msg":"Five years ago we lost. Today we have a chance to take it all back.<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"416fec66ca74e657b84aa066bd7b02310af84427","tid":1191004,"uid":78016,"like":41,"dislike":10,"score":31,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T16:37:43.000Z","msg":"真係毛管棟呀<br />\n大佬呀 遊行還遊行<br />\n唔好咁中二病啦<br />\n好想嘔呀<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59b9779cbbc5ade1da49916f24e7e107ca7f5e72","tid":1191004